--- src/db-analysis.js ---
@sig b6493058
export getDBSchema(dir:string)→parseProject,tables.map,tables.reduce|read parsed project to list all defined SQL tables and columns
export getTableUsage(dir:string,tableName)→parseProject,buildGraph,readers.some,readers.push,writers.some,writers.push|find readers and writers for tables using parsed graph edges
export getDBDeadTables(dir:string)→parseProject,buildGraph,referencedTables.add,referencedTables.has,schemaTables.filter,collectReferencedColumns|find schema tables not referenced by any read/write in code
collectReferencedColumns(parsed)→columns.add|heuristically collect all potential column names from code
PATTERNS: dependency graph analysis|heuristic DB column extraction
EDGE_CASES: hardcoded standard columns prevent false positive dead tables